text: Retzstadt is a community in the Main-Spessart district in the Regierungsbezirk of Lower Franconia (Unterfranken) in Bavaria, Germany and a member of the Verwaltungsgemeinschaft (Administrative Community) of Zellingen. == Geography == === Location === Retzstadt is in the Main-Spessart district in a side- valley of the Main, on the river Retz. The community has only the Gemarkung (traditional rural cadastral area) of Retzstadt. == References == Category:Main-Spessart
title: Retzstadt
